1. Clone the repo 
2. do a build check -> 
	mvn clean compile package
3. got to the server folder and do 
	mvn spring-boot:run     
to start the back-end application
    verify : 
	localhost:8080/
4. to start the front-end 
        npm install 
        ng server 
   and verify on 
	localhost:4200/

5 check all functionalities are working or not
	close the frontend server and	
		ng e2e
		ng test

6: if docker-compose file is given
	simply go to the dir where docker-compose file is present 
	docker-compose up 
	and we can access the app on localhost:4200


